            "content": "I submerge it in the pool but find no bubbles. After doing two passes I give up. I begin trying to listen for the hole. I’m about to give up when I hear a faint whistle. Wetting the mattress helps make the sound louder. I eventually find it. Hopefully this is the last hole. ",
